Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.64,op,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1\pos(375,280)}請回答我~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.83,op2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1}街道就像唱片般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:34.20,op2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1}每天承載着唱針播放出噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.78,op2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1}認識到被城市邊緣化的自己 令人厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:42.02,op2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1}錯位的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:44.23,op2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1}Good morning 陰到厭煩的sky sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:52.37,op2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1}那目光無法交匯的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:56.79,op2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.1}是否可以抵達
